object.Doubloon.name: Doubloon
object.Doubloon.description: A coin with only one purpose: to be sold.

object.Copper Seeds.description: Plant these in spring. Takes 10 days to mature.

object.Gold Seeds.description: Plant these in fall. Takes 20 days to mature.
object.Iridium Seeds.name: Iridium Seeds
object.Iridium Seeds.description: Plant these in winter. Takes 24 days to mature.
object.Iron Seeds.name: Iron Seeds
object.Iron Seeds.description: Plant these in summer. Takes 15 days to mature.
object.Doubloon Seeds.name: Doubloon Seeds
object.Doubloon Seeds.description: Plant these in fall. Takes 10 days to mature, and keeps producing after the first harvest.
object.Radioactive Seeds.name: Radioactive Seeds
object.Radioactive Seeds.description: Plant these in winter. Takes 24 days to mature.
